              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "-A gas proportional telescope consisting of :",
                " 1)a gas proportional chamber equivalent to 1 micro-m",
                "   thick Si",
                "   The chamber works with a gas mixture of Ar + 6% CO2",
                "   at 46 kPa pressure and 500 V voltage.",
                " 2)A surface-barrier semiconductor Si-Au detector",
                "   having an effective surface of 200 mm-2 and serving",
                "   for the energy analysis of alpha-particles.",
                "-The energy resolution of the gas proportional",
                " telescope for a-particles with E=5.48 keV is 160 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The energy calibration has been performed partly",
